Formerly (and internally) known as StardustLib.

NOTE TO SERVER OWNERS: this mod contains a second .pak! make sure this is loaded or client crashes may occur!

Library code and system features for the modded experience.
This mod contains the Quickbar; you don't need QuickbarMini with it.
This mod is a metaGUI provider (the primary one, in fact).

Other features:
- Costume system
- Navigation panel extension (fuel gauge, toolbar; per species options)
- Per-species intro cinematic system

If you're a modder, follow development here: 
https://github.com/zetaPRIME/sb.StardustSuite
